587
01:03:12,780 --> 01:03:14,580
Yeah, I'll help.

588
01:03:21,180 --> 01:03:23,660
- Did you live here?
- When I was young.

589
01:03:26,100 --> 01:03:27,900
There was grass everywhere then.

590
01:03:28,780 --> 01:03:30,500
Every year, it got drier.

591
01:03:31,220 --> 01:03:32,620
Mom was lonely.

592
01:03:33,780 --> 01:03:36,300
She likes people. Dad, doesn't need them.

593
01:03:41,700 --> 01:03:43,300
Lots of arguments.

594
01:03:46,100 --> 01:03:49,900
One day, Mom just ran off with this guy
who was passing through.

595
01:03:51,340 --> 01:03:52,340
Took me and my sister to the city.

596
01:03:52,380 --> 01:03:53,660
Took me and my sister to the city.

597
01:03:55,540 --> 01:03:56,980
Sydney first...

598
01:03:59,060 --> 01:04:01,700
eventually, all the way up to Kent.

599
01:04:09,140 --> 01:04:11,820
I've only seen Dad a couple times
since then.

600
01:04:16,340 --> 01:04:17,900
Where is she now?

601
01:04:18,900 --> 01:04:22,380
Mom? Up in Queensland.
With some new guy.

602
01:04:25,420 --> 01:04:27,620
My sister's in the Philippines, though.

603
01:04:32,660 --> 01:04:33,940
You think?

604
01:04:37,300 --> 01:04:39,220
We're not a close family.

605
01:06:04,540 --> 01:06:06,460
When you take this off...

606
01:06:08,020 --> 01:06:10,700
