626
01:08:28,780 --> 01:08:32,260
A bit hard to see with chicken soup
in my eyes, but maybe.

627
01:08:34,900 --> 01:08:36,580
Which way they went?

628
01:08:36,700 --> 01:08:38,380
Jesus, that was some good stuff.

629
01:08:39,060 --> 01:08:41,180
- Which way?
- Don't yell at me.

630
01:08:41,860 --> 01:08:44,700
- Which way!
- Fuck you.

631
01:08:48,740 --> 01:08:50,340
Stupid whore.

632
01:09:36,740 --> 01:09:38,460
- Good evening.
- Good evening.

633
01:09:38,540 --> 01:09:39,580
Beer.

634
01:09:39,660 --> 01:09:42,300
- Beer?
- Yes. Beer, please.

635
01:09:45,260 --> 01:09:46,900
Long way from home.

636
01:09:47,460 --> 01:09:48,700
Japan.

637
01:10:07,420 --> 01:10:10,020
Go on past me, you got plenty of room!

638
01:10:12,460 --> 01:10:13,940
Well, get fucked!

639
01:10:49,940 --> 01:10:51,500
