664
01:15:11,940 --> 01:15:14,100
- What's your name?
- Yukio.

665
01:15:16,700 --> 01:15:20,340
Well, there's a word. It's called karma.

666
01:15:22,300 --> 01:15:25,540
Sort of means you can do bad
or evil for a long time.

667
01:15:26,260 --> 01:15:30,020
But eventually,
eventually it'll catch up with you.

668
01:15:30,580 --> 01:15:32,260
And you'll be destroyed.

669
01:15:34,500 --> 01:15:36,180
When I was young...

670
01:15:38,500 --> 01:15:40,220
I was a bit of a lad.

671
01:15:41,220 --> 01:15:43,020
I did some bad things.

672
01:15:45,180 --> 01:15:48,740
Ended up in jail
for almost killing my best friend.

673
01:15:51,220 --> 01:15:53,380
He took my girlfriend from me.

674
01:15:56,340 --> 01:15:57,900
I served my time.

675
01:15:58,940 --> 01:16:03,460
It was bad karma, what I did.
He was my best friend.

676
01:16:06,420 --> 01:16:08,460
Now, it's caught up with me.

677
01:16:11,540 --> 01:16:13,300
Bad karma's this land.

678
01:16:16,180 --> 01:16:18,900
There's been a drought here for 10 years.

679
01:16:20,500 --> 01:16:22,740
And it'll continue until I die.

680
01:16:25,100 --> 01:16:26,660
But you, Yukio...

681
01:16:27,580 --> 01:16:30,300
Japan started the war against China...

682
01:16:31,140 --> 01:16:32,620
then the world.

683
01:16:33,780 --> 01:16:36,460
You lose the war. What happens?

684
01:16:37,940 --> 01:16:41,900
