Unfair.

685
01:16:43,420 --> 01:16:47,620
But your karma will change. Soon, Yukio...

686
01:16:48,980 --> 01:16:52,940
your tiny country,
with its millions of tiny people...

687
01:16:53,900 --> 01:16:55,980
will get the karma it deserves.

688
01:16:56,620 --> 01:16:59,500
Earthquakes, tidal waves...

689
01:17:01,060 --> 01:17:03,460
