690
01:17:03,940 --> 01:17:08,500
It will sink below the waves and drown.
As if it never existed.

691
01:17:09,300 --> 01:17:11,340
And you will die, Yukio.

692
01:17:12,220 --> 01:17:15,860
You will get the karma you deserve,
you understand?

693
01:17:16,820 --> 01:17:18,220
