700
01:18:58,420 --> 01:19:00,140
Going this way, pal?

701
01:19:05,940 --> 01:19:07,220
The beach.

702
01:19:08,340 --> 01:19:10,420
- What'd he say?
- I don't know.

703
01:19:10,540 --> 01:19:13,780
