705
01:19:17,140 --> 01:19:19,060
I want to go to beach.

706
01:19:19,500 --> 01:19:22,100
- The beach? You would like to see?
- Yes.

707
01:19:22,580 --> 01:19:24,500
- Yes.
- Okay, cool.

708
01:19:24,940 --> 01:19:28,020
Well, we'll drop you off in Porter.
