710
01:19:30,740 --> 01:19:32,660
To talk to my wife.

711
01:19:34,100 --> 01:19:36,060
Ain't been married long, eh?

712
01:19:40,620 --> 01:19:44,460
- What's "B and S Ball"?
- It's a dance for bachelors and spinsters.

713
01:19:45,220 --> 01:19:47,980
Is it a dance place
where you can wear good clothes?

714
01:19:48,020 --> 01:19:50,380
Yeah. Sunday best for the B and S.

715
01:20:17,820 --> 01:20:20,020
Hi. It's $25 each, thanks.

716
01:20:28,460 --> 01:20:30,740
Won't be a bachelor for long.

717
01:20:32,980 --> 01:20:36,060
- Last of our money.
- This is worth it.

718
01:20:36,580 --> 01:20:39,780
