won't let you ask me.

719
01:20:39,900 --> 01:20:41,860
Bachelor and spinster.

720
01:20:45,780 --> 01:20:47,820
Two beers. Thanks, mate.

721
01:20:49,660 --> 01:20:52,020
- May I have this dance?
- Yes.

722
01:20:52,340 --> 01:20:54,180
I'm a spinster tonight.

723
01:22:00,540 --> 01:22:01,700
Porter.

724
01:22:02,100 --> 01:22:04,140
